             was indicted for <rs id="t17981024-31-off174" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17981024-31-off174" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17981024-31-off174" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17981024-31-cd175" type="crimeDate">19th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17981024-31-off174 t17981024-31-cd175"></join>, a chest, containing 89 lb of tea, value 20l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17981024-31-victim256" type="victimName">
                     Matthew 
                     Bell
                  <interp inst="t17981024-31-victim256" type="surname" value="Bell"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17981024-31-victim256" type="given" value="Matthew"></interp>
